                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d907">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Azpíroz</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Spring Lake, N. J.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-09-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 14, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Secretary of Foreign Relations instructs me to transmit the deep sympathy of
                    the President and Government and people of Mexico with the President and
                    Government of the United States of America on occasion of the recent calamity at
                    Galveston. In doing so through you, I beg to add my own sympathy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">M. de Azpíroz.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
